    {
      "id": "el_20",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "D1 constant -> AP (linear)\nD2 constant -> Quadratic (squares)\nD3 constant -> Cubic\n\nWHY: Polynomial of degree n has constant\n  nth difference (like derivatives).\n\nEx: 1,4,9,16 → D1:3,5,7 → D2:2,2 constant\n  D2 constant = degree 2 = n^2 pattern\n\nD1 forms GP -> geometric-diff series\nKeep taking diffs until constant row!",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 20,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "D1 constant -> AP (linear)\nD2 constant -> Quadratic (squares)\nD3 constant -> Cubic\n\nWHY: Polynomial of degree n has constant\n  nth difference (like derivatives).\n\nEx: 1,4,9,16 → D1:3,5,7 → D2:2,2 constant\n  D2 constant = degree 2 = n^2 pattern\n\nD1 forms GP -> geometric-diff series\nKeep taking diffs until constant row!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
