    {
      "id": "el_26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 704,
      "width": 425,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Diffs: 8-5=3, 11-8=3, 14-11=3, 17-14=3\nStep 2: Constant diff d=3 -> AP\nStep 3: Next = 17+3 = 20\n\n  5 ──+3──> 8 ──+3──> 11 ──+3──> 14 ──+3──> 17 ──+3──> [20]\n\nTRICK:\na(n) = a + (n-1)d = 5 + 5x3 = 20\nOr just: last + d = 17+3 = 20\n\nAnswer: 20 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
