      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Diffs: 8-5=3, 11-8=3, 14-11=3, 17-14=3\nStep 2: Constant diff d=3 -> AP\nStep 3: Next = 17+3 = 20\n\n  5 ──+3──> 8 ──+3──> 11 ──+3──> 14 ──+3──> 17 ──+3──> [20]\n\nTRICK:\na(n) = a + (n-1)d = 5 + 5x3 = 20\nOr just: last + d = 17+3 = 20\n\nAnswer: 20 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
