    {
      "id": "el_31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 704,
      "width": 425,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Ratios: 6/3=2, 12/6=2, 24/12=2, 48/24=2\nStep 2: Constant ratio r=2 -> GP\nStep 3: Next = 48x2 = 96\n\n  3 ──x2──> 6 ──x2──> 12 ──x2──> 24 ──x2──> 48 ──x2──> [96]\n\nTRICK:\na(n) = a x r^(n-1) = 3 x 2^5 = 96\nOr just: last x r = 48x2 = 96\n\nAnswer: 96 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
