      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Ratios: 6/3=2, 12/6=2, 24/12=2, 48/24=2\nStep 2: Constant ratio r=2 -> GP\nStep 3: Next = 48x2 = 96\n\n  3 ──x2──> 6 ──x2──> 12 ──x2──> 24 ──x2──> 48 ──x2──> [96]\n\nTRICK:\na(n) = a x r^(n-1) = 3 x 2^5 = 96\nOr just: last x r = 48x2 = 96\n\nAnswer: 96 ✓",
