    {
      "id": "el_36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 704,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1: 1,3,5,7,9 -> AP with d=2\nStep 2: Next D1 = 9+2 = 11\nStep 3: Next term = 26+11 = 37\n\n  Row 0:  1    2    5   10   17   26   [37]\n  D1:       1    3    5    7    9   [11]\n  D2:         2    2    2    2   [2]  <- constant!\n\nTRICK:\nPattern: n^2 + 1 for n=0,1,2,3,4,5,6\n6^2 + 1 = 37\nD2 constant -> square-based series!\n\nAnswer: 37 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
