      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1: 1,3,5,7,9 -> AP with d=2\nStep 2: Next D1 = 9+2 = 11\nStep 3: Next term = 26+11 = 37\n\n  Row 0:  1    2    5   10   17   26   [37]\n  D1:       1    3    5    7    9   [11]\n  D2:         2    2    2    2   [2]  <- constant!\n\nTRICK:\nPattern: n^2 + 1 for n=0,1,2,3,4,5,6\n6^2 + 1 = 37\nD2 constant -> square-based series!\n\nAnswer: 37 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
