    {
      "id": "el_46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1086,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Odd positions:  3,7,11,15 -> AP d=4\nStep 2: Even positions: 5,10,15,? -> AP d=5\nStep 3: Next is pos 8 (even) = 15+5 = 20\n\n  Pos:  1   2   3   4    5    6    7   8\n        3   5   7   10   11   15   15  [?]\n  Odd:  3 ──+4──> 7 ──+4──> 11 ──+4──> 15\n  Even:   5 ──+5──> 10 ──+5──> 15 ──+5──> [20]\n\nTRICK:\nNo single pattern? Split odd/even positions!\nTwo interleaved series, solve each.\n\nAnswer: 20 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
