        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Odd positions:  3,7,11,15 -> AP d=4\nStep 2: Even positions: 5,10,15,? -> AP d=5\nStep 3: Next is pos 8 (even) = 15+5 = 20\n\n  Pos:  1   2   3   4    5    6    7   8\n        3   5   7   10   11   15   15  [?]\n  Odd:  3 ──+4──> 7 ──+4──> 11 ──+4──> 15\n  Even:   5 ──+5──> 10 ──+5──> 15 ──+5──> [20]\n\nTRICK:\nNo single pattern? Split odd/even positions!\nTwo interleaved series, solve each.\n\nAnswer: 20 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
