    {
      "id": "el_51",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1086,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1: 3,5,7,9,11 -> AP d=2\nStep 2: D2: 2,2,2,2 -> constant!\nStep 3: Next D1 = 13, next = 37+13 = 50\n\n  n:    1    2    3    4    5    6    [7]\n  n^2+1: 2    5   10   17   26   37   [50]\n  D1:      3    5    7    9   11   [13]\n  D2:        2    2    2    2   [2]\n\nTRICK:\nPattern: n^2 + 1\n7^2 + 1 = 49+1 = 50\nD2 constant = always a square-based series.\n\nAnswer: 50 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
