    {
      "id": "el_66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1467,
      "width": 461,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Convert: A=1, C=3, E=5, G=7, I=9\nStep 2: Diffs: +2, +2, +2, +2 -> AP\nStep 3: Next = 9+2 = 11 = K\n\n  A(1) ─+2─> C(3) ─+2─> E(5) ─+2─> G(7) ─+2─> I(9) ─+2─> [K(11)]\n\nTRICK:\nAlways convert letters to numbers first!\nSolve as number series, convert back.\nWrap: after Z(26) -> A(1) [mod 26]\n\nAnswer: K ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
