        "type_9"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Convert: A=1, C=3, E=5, G=7, I=9\nStep 2: Diffs: +2, +2, +2, +2 -> AP\nStep 3: Next = 9+2 = 11 = K\n\n  A(1) ─+2─> C(3) ─+2─> E(5) ─+2─> G(7) ─+2─> I(9) ─+2─> [K(11)]\n\nTRICK:\nAlways convert letters to numbers first!\nSolve as number series, convert back.\nWrap: after Z(26) -> A(1) [mod 26]\n\nAnswer: K ✓",
