      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1: 3,5,7,7,13,13\nStep 2: Expected D1: 3,5,7,9,11,13 (AP d=2)\nStep 3: 7 repeats at pos 4-5 -> pos 5 wrong\nStep 4: 24 should be 17+9 = 26\n\n  2   5  10  17  24  37  50   <- given\n  D1:  3   5   7  [7] 13  13\n  Expected:  3   5   7  [9] 11  13  <- AP d=2\n                        ^^ WRONG!\n  Fix: 17+9 = 26, not 24\n\nTRICK:\nFind the pattern break in D1.\nReplace wrong term to restore the AP.\nCorrected: 2,5,10,17,26,37,50\n\nAnswer: 24 is wrong, should be 26 ✓",
