      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: D1: 4, 8, ?, ?, 64\nStep 2: D1 looks like GP: 4,8,16,32,64 (x2)\nStep 3: 15+16 = 31. Verify: 63-32 = 31 ✓\n\n  3    7    15    [?]    63    127\n  D1:  4     8    [16]    32     64   (GP x2)\n       └─x2─┘└─x2─┘ └─x2─┘ └─x2─┘\n  Missing = 15+16 = 31\n\nTRICK:\nPattern: 2^n - 1 for n=2,3,4,5,6,7\n2^5 - 1 = 31\n\nAnswer: 31 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
