      "x": 65,
      "y": 2303,
      "width": 490,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 2x2-1=3, 3x2-1=5, 5x2-1=9\nStep 2: 9x2-1=17, 17x2-1=33\nStep 3: Pattern: each = prev x 2 - 1\n\n  2 ─x2-1─> 3 ─x2-1─> 5 ─x2-1─> 9 ─x2-1─> 17 ─x2-1─> 33 ─x2-1─> [65]\n\nTRICK:\nRatio ~2? Try x2+1 or x2-1.\nNext = 33x2-1 = 65\nCommon patterns: xN+C, xN-C\n\nAnswer: 65 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
