    {
      "id": "el_91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2303,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Find relation: 2 -> 8\nStep 2: 2^3 = 8 (cube)\nStep 3: Apply same: 3^3 = 27\n\n  2 : 8  ::  3 : [?]\n  |   |      |    |\n  n   n^3    n    n^3\n  2   2^3=8  3   3^3=[27]\n\nTRICK:\nCheck common rules in order:\nn^2, n^3, 2n, n^2+1, n(n+1), n^2-1\n2^3=8 matches -> 3^3=27\n\nAnswer: 27 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
