    {
      "id": "el_96",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2303,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Pairs: (12,21) (34,43) (56,?)\nStep 2: Each pair: number + its reverse\nStep 3: Base: 12,34,56 (+22 each)\n  Next = reverse of 56 = 65\n\n  12 -> 21 , 34 -> 43 , 56 -> [65]\n  |    rev   |    rev   |     rev\n  Base: 12 ──+22──> 34 ──+22──> 56\n\nTRICK:\nAlternating: normal, reversed, normal...\nBase series +22: 12,34,56,78...\nOdd pos=normal, even pos=reversed digits.\n\nAnswer: 65 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
